{"tid":2061371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚險重溫】汪 明 荃 台 上 斷 吊 帶 處 變 不 驚 繼 續 獻 唱","createTime":"2020-06-12T10:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T13:37:41.000Z","uid":24160,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"26e4cf271671409e5078dab77588680847a329d5","tid":2061371,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.sinaimg.cn/ent/j/2009-04-19/U3124P28T3D2480248F326DT20090419113409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Fj%2F2009-04-19%2FU3124P28T3D2480248F326DT20090419113409.jpg&h=e0b87d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐左邊吊帶突然斷開，不過她處變不驚，繼續獻唱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.sinaimg.cn/ent/j/2009-04-19/U3124P28T3D2480248F329DT20090419113409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Fj%2F2009-04-19%2FU3124P28T3D2480248F329DT20090419113409.jpg&h=fff3b111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅家英跪地獻花求婚，不過被阿姐拒絕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i3.sinaimg.cn/ent/j/2009-04-19/U3124P28T3D2480248F328DT20090419113409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Fj%2F2009-04-19%2FU3124P28T3D2480248F328DT20090419113409.jpg&h=a1449ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅家英欲親嘴再遭阿姐以花隔開，實在掃興<br />\n<br />\n新浪娛樂訊北京時間4月19日消息，據香港媒體報導，汪明荃領銜主演的歌舞喜劇4月17日晚在香港公演，獻唱時她的晚裝斷了一邊吊帶，不過阿姐處變不驚，繼續演出。在受訪時，她對沒有做媽媽流露遺憾之意。<br />\n<br />\n  汪明荃領銜主演的百老匯式歌舞喜劇《真係阿姐&mdash;汪明荃》前晚(4月17日晚)在香港公演，吸引胡杏兒一家、翁嘉穗夫婦、趙雅芝夫婦等捧場，阿姐坐在大吊燈上出場，勁歌熱舞，男友羅家英則不斷大搞氣氛，首先身穿大紅心衛衣出場，並替阿姐按摩溫馨一番，又以&ldquo;傻豬豬&rdquo;及&ldquo;Baby&rdquo;稱呼阿姐，逗得台下笑聲連連，隨後羅家英手拿道具花唱出《我向你求婚》向阿姐求婚，現場也播出《結婚進行曲》來配合。<br />\n<br />\n  阿姐在一段16分鐘的剖白環節中大談人生經歷，直言對沒能當上媽媽導致不懂得與小朋友溝通感到遺憾。然後阿姐再換上一襲黑色吊帶晚裝獻唱經典金曲，但期間左邊吊帶突然斷開，不過見慣大場面的她處變不驚，繼續演出。<br />\n<br />\n  事後問阿姐是不是很想做媽咪，她說：&ldquo;女人能有生育過程，對後代來說是好一點的。&rdquo;&ldquo;當時是不是因為事業沒有生BB？&rdquo;&ldquo;這個不能強求。&rdquo;&ldquo;領養吧！&rdquo;&ldquo;又不是自己生的，不是那種感覺，而且年紀大了都不讓領養啦！&rdquo;談到羅家英在台上求婚，但阿姐還沒有答應，問她末場再度上演時會不會答應？阿姐笑笑表示不會。<br />\n<br />\n2009年04月19日11:34 <br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/j/2009-04-19/11342480248.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.sina.com.cn%2Fj%2F2009-04-19%2F11342480248.shtml&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=774a45b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ent.sina.com.cn/j/2009-04-19/11342480248.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"75f5a63caf1e9465084a7b0b27c481cbaa923d1b","tid":2061371,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCdEHqp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCdEHqp.gif&h=afb3860e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffe7234932d576213cda497b902d2ee728158a86","tid":2061371,"uid":194326,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯汪明荃上吊"},{"pid":"fe5e4b8dad532f0b05a3f6f2654ac5404af44c9e","tid":2061371,"uid":24160,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ffe7234932d576213cda497b902d2ee728158a86","tid":2061371,"uid":194326,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯汪明荃上吊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cAg0Day.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcAg0Day.gif&h=7884fa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"658bd289c62c7f338386c3470d8c714b1598a536","tid":2061371,"uid":52819,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"台下觀眾驚過佢啦"},{"pid":"e5f5babf85a36834efd7b50f8a44dab9f55cb781","tid":2061371,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見蛆BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57c45e3737ab63123d0e8d53c5b9ebbec31eeed","tid":2061371,"uid":24160,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T10:34:18.000Z","msg":"認真斷帶示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/34RAKQ6.